      <h2>Maintenance and Lubrication</h2>

      <div class="warning">
        These handpieces do not require any lubrication. Putting oil or grease into the front or back will damage the pre-lubricated ball bearings.
      </div>

      <p>Periodically remove the chuck nut and collet and clean the collet holder seat and threads of dust or debris with a bristle brush or air gun.</p>

